Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still here thanks to Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can take you \Nall down with this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law and Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NTheir relationship began 16 years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knowing his days were numbered,\NLaw came to join the Don Quixote Family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There, he met the silent, \Nchild-hating Corazon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There he is! Corazon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My parents, young sister,\Nand everybody from the church were dead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that idiot is alive - it's not fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They won't know if I keep quiet.{\i0}
