Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:20.90,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SPIDER MILES - A PORT TOWN IN THE NORTH BLUE\N16 YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're a Celestial Dragon family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're "former" Celestial Dragons!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy won't do anything \Neven if we kill them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The admirals won't come, either!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I got a chance to retaliate!\NI thought I'd have to bear it silently all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Break all their bones with a hammer!\N--Shoot a thousand arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't kill them so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep them alive long enough\Nto make them suffer and suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! No slap-on-the-wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I wanna get my revenge on them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sons were only five\Nand two years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all they did was cut across the \Npath of the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for that reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My enslaved daughter came \Nhome looking horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand without speaking a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she killed herself three days later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once your slave!\NAnd my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you jerks... \NBecause of you jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't give a damn about our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the Heavenly \NTribute we pay to you fools,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nmy country was destroyed by famine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone became skin and bones, and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are like gods, aren't you?!\NYou're different from humans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I bet this won't kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doffy!\N--Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you treat us humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,worse than worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what it is like to \Nbe in pain or grief or agony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Celestial Dragons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
