Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be the \Nlast person to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you give \Nup your status as a god
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand reduce yourself to a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ST. DON QUIXOTE HOMING\NTHE WORLD NOBLE (CELESTIAL DRAGON)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a human. Since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we are too-{\i1}eh{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sacrilege!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think we Celestial Dragons are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor! You've always been heretical!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you think.\NHumans are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way more satisfying to\Nlive as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eek! What did you say?!\N--So rude-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of Mariejois now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take you farther than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the north end.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A non-member nation of the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An adequate house and assets\Nare ready for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. That's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll collect\Nyour Celestial Dragon ID chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live a humble life here,\Nall four of us as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to unpack first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Where are the slaves-{\i1}eh{\i0}?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the slaves put away stuff-{\i1}eh{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there aren't any,\Nlet's go buy some-{\i1}eh{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy. Rocinante.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to teach you from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great, Doffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna wear these!\NI look like a slave-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Father, I don't want them-{\i1}eh{\i0}!\NI'll stink if I wear these-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:11:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, we're gonna live\Nas humans from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lead a life far richer than\Nthe life in Mariejois.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean by "rich" is\Nnot having so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your two apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to purchase some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You don't look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I moved here from Mariejois recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Don Quixote Homing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mariejois...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you a Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cast that title aside.\NI am a human from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to become friends with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you fall down on your knees?!\NYou fools are disrespectful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just cut across in front of me, didn't you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, get a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!\NHey, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the Celestial Dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Find them!\N--Hang them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, why don't they fall down\Non their knees-eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not in here! They must've run!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them! I don't think \Nthey got too far yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill them!\NKeep them alive and let them suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get several centuries worth of revenge\Nout of that family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father! Why do they come after us-eh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be thankful\Nto be out of the rain here at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People around here haven't \Nheard about us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's stay here for a while...\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I live in such a dirty place-{\i1}eh{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are bugs inside the house!\NThe smell here makes me sick-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should still be around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them as soon as you find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta run! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't expect it'd turn out this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too optimistic.\NPlease! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just my wife and children are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWould you let them go back to Mariejois?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, we all get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was your choice-eh.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take back something you gave up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever call me again!\NYou're no more than a human!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bread thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father! For the first time in my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel pain-eh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the first time in my life,\NI'm hungry-eh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat fast, Rocy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, we brought you some food-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy. Rocy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NI don't feel quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother is dead-eh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my boys! Just take me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look what you've done-eh!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-sama, we caught Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he suddenly decided to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was already at the port-{\i1}in{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll start torturing him\Nfor stabbing Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Law is a poor boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Corazon...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! He didn't die!\NThen, will I get killed for nothing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shut Buffalo's mouth\Nby buying him an ice cream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but he told Doflamingo himself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure the blade went through his body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can he act like he's fine?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you in for just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to welcome you to the \NDoflamingo Family officially.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Family-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you went through \Nsuch a horrible experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you got that incomparable, \Nhateful look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the "quality."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees potential in your future!\NYoung Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} is a visionary man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't he know\Nwhat I did to Corazon yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? He can tell him by writing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he up to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he sees future potential in me,\NI will die in three years anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We specialize in the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NAnd we handle the Devil Fruits, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And some of those Fruits have\Npowers that are beyond human knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a Fruit\Nthat could cure your disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life could be saved by \Na Devil Fruit we come across
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the three years you have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will train you to become my \Nright-hand man 10 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ENEMY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--An enemy hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I FINISHED HIM OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Get it treated, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he just... cover up for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he thinking, really?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Towards Reverse Mountain in the southeast,\Nwe'll keep moving our base
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and expanding our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TWO YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you our real names!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? I'm not interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so uncool! You're no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have fun, I'll die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite a lot of white parts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if\NI can live another year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may die sooner than I calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, if you have a real name,\Ntell us-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll tell the Young Master\Nyou stabbed Cora-{\i1}san{\i0} two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar D. Water Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't tell that name\Nto anybody, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't go by a code name like you two\Nso it's just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D." is a secret name, \N"Water" is a true name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NFor generations, my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How boring! This is not fun at all.\N--Yeah-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys asked me repeatedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Corazon!\NWhat do you want?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's gonna get beaten again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0} looked scarier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Corazon?!\NDo you wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said before, was it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh? Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret name "D"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, you need to get out of here.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! You shouldn't be around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As Law's moment of death approaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he and Corazon set off on a journey \Nto look for a cure for his disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the long, painful journey,\NCorazon starts pouring out his heart in tears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which deepens the bond between the two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Rocky Road! Law and \NCorazon's Journey of Life!"
